reviews.review_text: a slight improvement over the Jim Wise copy The sound is a little cleaner.  The levels are a little lower, so there's less distortion, and also a little less crowd noise.  Unfortunately, you still can't hear much of Brent during Playin' after he switches to the electric piano.  I already reviewed this gem of a show on the Wise copy.
